Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 確認到大量水雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說為什麼你會在這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有少主的地方就有我猿伴隨左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了少主能在這個收視率高的餘興節目中能優美地勝出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會加倍努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的情況 能多一個戰鬥力就是一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.36,0:00:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…留奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿下餘興節目 獎金Get！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拿下之時 我把百萬獎金全送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼上性命去戰鬥吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就保持這個速度衝上去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被騙了 猿！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左舷中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右舷也中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.43,0:00:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺改變航向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒功夫迂迴了 只有正面突破
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會有水雷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:01:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴族…源羲魚玩起來就不知分寸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羲魚是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超難纏的 女癖異常的變態貴族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比黑幫還要難對付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦出什麼事的話 我絕對不會放過…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.26,0:01:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混賬 本小姐可不會輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留…留奈 你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.15,0:01:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看 江戶前組的歌姬啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.95,0:01:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？孩子他媽 永澄呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 看來短時間回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是男生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有什麼花樣都放馬過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ほんならな 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&H000000&\3c&Hffffff&\shad0}衝出逆境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:10.46,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,源家海底王宮 海上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:14.13,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,同海底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我碎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 這一拳應該…呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.59,0:02:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連老大的拳頭都打不碎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是裝了鑽石還是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這狀況其他部分應該也都封死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這回還真是挺糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個變態人渣貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他敢碰小姐一根指頭 俺就把他射成蜂窩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 卷！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣很危險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜點 卷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大姐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在這裏鬧也起不了任何作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 設身處地為小姐著想的話 俺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俺就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿蓮！你就不擔心小燦了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我帶她過來的 都怪我那麼輕率地帶小燦過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 這不是大姐頭的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定得做些什麼 豪三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定得想辦法對付那王八羔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的是這女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦真是激和諧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超可愛啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~跟我比起來誰更可愛一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羲魚 又要「那個」了嗎 你決定是那個女孩了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然決定了 這回沒準要玩真結婚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 羲魚 你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我一直都覺得瀨戶內組的小燦很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然帶了她過來 我還沒對她下手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我多pure love~這就是「純愛」~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人家怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是你心中第一位的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家可是門第很高的貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重婚什麼的可是沒關係的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真和諧 羲魚你真是個天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人果然是豐富多彩啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很強大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她是那個黑幫的女兒  不會有麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 他們這些地痞哪裏敢跟貴族作對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是最強的呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小明乃~怎麼那麼掃興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起來Happy啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羲魚大人…做得太過火的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼向京都的總部報告？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？我不懂你說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子就是不想跟京都那些老傢伙\N一塊才會到這種鄉下地方建個別墅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羲魚果然和諧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 在這裏老子說的話就是法律 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說 按照小明乃的家規 是絕對不能違抗貴族的命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修煉劍士大人~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小明乃~到小燦那裏去幫她打扮打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子的結婚儀式 過一下很快就要開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很好笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦 小燦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突擊開始 請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全體人員 做好抗衝擊準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要突擊啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢房被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孑孓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警衛在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的warning了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:49.17,Default2,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你撞的時候就不能找個好點的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害的餘興節目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羲魚！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是幹什麼的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這不是跑到了敵人的正中間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道這裏是源羲魚大人的海底王宮還敢來鬧事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴 你們這些下等人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在這裏的是 是三河財團的下一任當家---三河海大人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興致好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面子還真大 你們這些嘍囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我讓路！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼就直接衝過去啊 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跟上少爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正義在我們三河家這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看源字軍啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾開 別擋路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀~這戰鬥場面還真壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾開 你這色猴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 我要來做掩護啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Open your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人魚 古代歌詞 「戰爭之詩」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二版
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 笨蛋 別唱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都變成不堪入目的慘劇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死啦 我要死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 為什麼就我一個沒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:04.50,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音抗性能力 Lv Max
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,技能已發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羲魚一定是在這裏面的大堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去！僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 香檳酒都灑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才搖得那麼厲害是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氣氛都變差了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~掃興了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了 我找小燦玩去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到結婚再搞 太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羲魚是在這裏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管什麼貴不貴族的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不會讓你隨意胡搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會是做小燦老公的那個小鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到我羲魚家有何貴幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事就快點搞定然後滾蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你？把小燦還我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？你從埼玉趕過來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真夠死纏爛打啊 噁心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才噁心 別搞笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃~這傢伙不會是認真的吧 真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小明乃 拜託你幹掉他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知火 你在這裏幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知火？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是修煉劍士 絕不能違抗貴族的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 小燦以後就歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然她是被你「開發過」的二手貨 這點我有點不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？「開發過」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的？你還沒對她下手？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早說啊！這太爽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別開國際玩笑啊 你這人渣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知火…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人是有「很多很多事情的」小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小明乃也是啊 連那些都不懂的話 這樣可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知火 不能把小燦交給那種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來 人魚和人類結合這種事情是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 別跟他白費唇舌了 快手快腳給他個痛快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄瀨戶燦 向他低頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的話 羲魚大人還能繞你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯 我可是寬大為懷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼才會放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？快放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快說放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還在說什麼夢話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是為了幹這種事才當劍士的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這樣真的沒所謂嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不可以違背自己的意願而揮劍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿潮永澄 為義氣 吾出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今宵 明星的光芒 不含一絲迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 天帝之劍嗎？別太囂張了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼 也要為寫檢討書的我想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 跟你哥一個樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿潮永澄 把你的信念貫徹給我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 從一開始我就打算這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能把小燦交給那種人渣 絕對的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 你們真讓人火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之你們就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了？搖得這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…  這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的寵物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它可是雜食類的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論人類還是人魚 照單全吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是很厲害啊 ha ha ha
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「絕對」…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話說的不錯嘛 孑孓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岳父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別叫我岳父啊！你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然敢小瞧老子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我Call你們要立刻接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羲魚大人 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羲魚大人 包給你搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這群人是幹啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來就靠你們啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站…站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes 羲魚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們親衛隊 一定搞定他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的 超高壓水鐵炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小卷！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得不錯嘛 海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄 你確實讓我看到男子氣概了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能吃永澄的 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政先生 藤代先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄 你來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岳母大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！讓這些貴族的走狗 嘗嘗瀨戶內組的厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳扭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 還真的吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~真是毫不手軟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來就交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦由我來接回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要把她接回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦她 在暑假的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道救了我之後就得死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還是救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管我只是一個毫不相干的陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦教會了我 比起自己的生命更重要的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 瀨戶內人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成為跟小燦相稱的男人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把信念 貫徹到底！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天很帥哦 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼！別忘了你剛說的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別想過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在本地是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擋路！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧！滿潮永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠 竟然還有第二條
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀨戶蓮 跟音叉劍合體攻擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老娘的聲音可是 很昂貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有第三條！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I Shall Return
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江戶前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼穿水手服？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是外資企業
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟京都的貴族毫不相干！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謎之音：無敵大鐵人FX
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 用鐵拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害啊~好燒錢的餘興節目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用死光！射死這些畜生！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真夠痛 一個兩個都跑來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子對那些熱血混球最火大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂~小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫 這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是難纏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你對她幹了些什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才正要干呢 別來壞我好事！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明這麼弱就別跑來跟魚人貴族作對 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過讓她順從了一點罷了 她已經聽不到你的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人魚的秘寶 這不是人類能招架的 不過貌似對你沒效呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然用那種東西把小燦弄成那樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她胡鬧起來的話 可是很麻煩的~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:16:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼 怎麼可能打得過我這個魚人貴族嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 我不會讓你這傢伙為所欲為的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噴~真是很好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小燦的面前還那麼遜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦…小燦 我來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 這還是我們第一次吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 下次我會把襪子的裏面翻出來的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會把紙巾放在牛仔褲口袋裏面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碗碟也會先洗過再放了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…那種告別 那種告別 我絕對不承認啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 你好煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在我身邊 不要走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你煩死了 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到了 永澄的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然之前一直都是一片空白 什麼都聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我聽到永澄在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄叫我「哪都不要去」我聽到了這個呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們別掃興好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫 為了得到一個女人 必須要用這麼卑鄙的手段嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦 超煩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒想到你是個這麼煩的女人 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛 我要殺了你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼可以用槍指著女生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可以用槍指著小燦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄 我現在就唱 「英雄之詩」…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永~澄！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說過了嘛 我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在 可是前所未有的憤怒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿潮永澄史上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大的憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄 沒有英雄之詩 竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要小燦在我身邊 力量就不斷涌現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要小燦在我身邊 我就會無限變強！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.62,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,自律型超戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些韌魚害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 風暴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風暴來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很遜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太逆天了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.65,0:19:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我聽好了 羲魚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真男人是寫作「仁俠」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把一切托付給男人是寫作「任俠」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫是寫作「仁/任俠」但讀作「人魚」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這群傢伙搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是個身為仁俠不可放任的歪門邪道！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要拼了命過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拚命就是寫作「必定會死」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26}{\pos(280,434)}「必死」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你這個沒有必死的覺悟的男人 永澄是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滅殺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是小燦的份！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是小燦的份！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戶的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還是小燦的份！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是 小燦的份啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處決
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫁~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 原來是鯰魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？鯰魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我的眼 我的眼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羲魚大人 不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是鯰魚啊 鯰魚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的 超受歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太丟臉了 我鄙視你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羲魚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事我要向京都報告才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你鬧得太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭啊 小燦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要道歉的 其實是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦 我 會更加更加努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你 就一直留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小女子未經世事 還請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄~快來吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我睡過頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄 就算叫都不肯起床…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早就不修邊幅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了 留奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.76,0:22:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你離小燦的理想愛人又進一步了呢 永澄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小~燦~去上學咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄 太有肌肉feel了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們這班遲到慣犯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小巡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是安全上壘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多講無益 要不要我教你社會的規矩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放過我們吧 別抓我們 警察大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小燦 屬於我跟小燦美妙的新一周又開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 配角 快去買紅茶…我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 真惱人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:22:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永澄大人 辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝觀看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:49.60,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,ふとした瞬間に運命の 齒車は回り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:55.66,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,氣紛れなんかじゃない 確かな 今日に變わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.23,0:22:01.56,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,答えはいつだって 目の前で 手招いてないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.19,0:22:07.48,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,貴方とならば 探せると 信じてみたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:19.52,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,喜び悲しみ すべてがきっと 道標になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:31.51,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,囁きかけてくる オレンジの空は 遙かに遠く、近く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.15,0:22:43.60,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,囁きかけてくる オレンジの海に 私は明日への光 見つけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:48.72,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,囁きかけてくる オレンジの空は Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:23:06.92,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,囁きかけてくる オレンジの海に 貴方へと續く想い抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:15.84,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,私は明日への光 見つけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:48.19,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,さぁ いま
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:51.46,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,心は楔に變わる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:55.01,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,さぁ いま
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:58.17,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,ことばも鋼にできる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:01.14,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,信じ續ければ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.85,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,壁はかならず崩れる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:11.84,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,深い思いに きっと答えがある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:17.73,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,それはここにもある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:25.24,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,それは闇へと きらきら光りだす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,へぇ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:40.09,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたは愛を生みだせる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,へぇ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:59.32,in_jap,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたは愛に生まれたから
